    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Holds all data for a acceleration structure build command. The structure allows to issue builds of top and bottom structures at the same time. The execution order of the data structure is as follows: 1) Build all opacity micro map triangle arrays 2) Flush 1) 3) Build all bottom level structures 4) Flush 3), when requested 5) Build all top level structures 6) Flush 5), when requested </para>
    </detaileddescription>
